ass=\"hkgmoji\" />  無水都柯篤尿照下個樣啦！矮柒毒撚 ！"},{"pid":"62888ebe71bd9e0a725e41dd90e878b198284d05","tid":441444,"uid":16959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過一排咪又係諗番起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要呢排秋風起就仲掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講好左秋天一齊去行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一涷就好想有個人係身邊攬下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c35bc5358d80c62fc42cb09b2ce60a17135708d","tid":441444,"uid":16959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:28:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己都可以好好地 個天唔會跌 個地唔會陷<br />\n諗起好正常 唯有做其他野麻木自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n忙個時咪無嘢<br />\n一靜落黎就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55437d7ae7f1bbd3c4d3516af0d4fe65f0d7ff5","tid":441444,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:29:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>介唔介意交換tg傾偈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又引晒d垃圾厹出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無水都柯篤尿照下個樣啦！矮柒毒撚 ！</blockquote><br />\n汪"},{"pid":"13b7a2e915078f491db810776db9810630afdf93","tid":441444,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己都可以好好地 個天唔會跌 個地唔會陷<br />\n諗起好正常 唯有做其他野麻木自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n忙個時咪無嘢<br />\n一靜落黎就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時係咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵d野忙下啦 會過去的<br />\n加油呀"},{"pid":"110cd9ca090b0d80cb4215fbcd14fe10aa7f99b9","tid":441444,"uid":907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:45:05.000Z","msg":"如果佢話後悔呢？"},{"pid":"b08e8f17736b870f1ef25fd236bba075edcff0b9","tid":441444,"uid":83992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:55:40.000Z","msg":"忙果陣還好 到左夜晚就仆街死 <br />\n<br />\n黎緊又聖誕喇 屌 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e8babfcbd4d44a2952c734db5677525fd40899","tid":441444,"uid":154484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:57:05.000Z","msg":"做下自己中意做既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分散下注意力<br />\n仲有仲有千其唔好聽失戀歌！"},{"pid":"df5ede9aa7d38e64fe95ed34e2071e93e6d6a0d8","tid":441444,"uid":50614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T18:00:50.000Z","msg":"共勉之<br />\n我都係琴日分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵啲野做下比自己散心<br />\n你有冇自己嘅興趣？<br />\n可能你地一齊果陣 你有嘅興趣放低左<br />\n依家可以拎翻起啲興趣<br />\n同埋可以嘅話 同朋友傾下計 比自己放鬆下<br />\n連登都仲有好多人可以陪你傾計啊"},{"pid":"0ecb43ab068de8e0bd0c67d66ea002bc6e92c254","tid":441444,"uid":16959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T19:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共勉之<br />\n我都係琴日分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵啲野做下比自己散心<br />\n你有冇自己嘅興趣？<br />\n可能你地一齊果陣 你有嘅興趣放低左<br />\n依家可以拎翻起啲興趣<br />\n同埋可以嘅話 同朋友傾下計 比自己放鬆下<br />\n連登都仲有好多人可以陪你傾計啊</blockquote><br />\n最緊要真係唔好將啲負面情緒收收埋埋<br />\n搵朋友傾又好<br />\n飲下酒又好<br />\n一定要講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2d7500712c7cbca14ea6f089e4c202fa848b50","tid":441444,"uid":95759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己都可以好好地 個天唔會跌 個地唔會陷<br />\n諗起好正常 唯有做其他野麻木自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n忙個時咪無嘢<br />\n一靜落黎就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時係咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵d野忙下啦 會過去的<br />\n加油呀</blockquote><br />\n我應唔應該del 曬佢啲野，好似會容易啲忘記佢，同時又唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5b632330904f865a9e4f7b335c17c5ed41d8ed","tid":441444,"uid":95759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢話後悔呢？</blockquote><br />\n唔會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係佢揀既"},{"pid":"2e3a9b90047a1a5c97a09b32ee4fa596e640cd84","tid":441444,"uid":95759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:38:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>共勉之<br />\n我都係琴日分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵啲野做下比自己散心<br />\n你有冇自己嘅興趣？<br />\n可能你地一齊果陣 你有嘅興趣放低左<br />\n依家可以拎翻起啲興趣<br />\n同埋可以嘅話 同朋友傾下計 比自己放鬆下<br />\n連登都仲有好多人可以陪你傾計啊</blockquote><br />\n最緊要真係唔好將啲負面情緒收收埋埋<br />\n搵朋友傾又好<br />\n飲下酒又好<br />\n一定要講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喊到雙眼皮都冇埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喊夠啦"},{"pid":"cde4aad2e479fb7b4bd34d57f8e9edcbf4be6929","tid":441444,"uid":95759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:39:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>忙果陣還好 到左夜晚就仆街死 <br />\n<br />\n黎緊又聖誕喇 屌 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一靜個腦就自動波諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff987a88831d369ab48c1ca8250714adf6fd404","tid":441444,"uid":153109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:40:13.000Z","msg":"上星期分左<br />\n前幾日自己去唱k 喊到仆街<br />\n之後個人好好多了<br />\n但呢幾日訓訓下都會無啦啦自己喊"},{"pid":"6a9b08c090f54e952a59345284a1234a270612dd","tid":441444,"uid":95759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:51:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上星期分左<br />\n前幾日自己去唱k 喊到仆街<br />\n之後個人好好多了<br />\n但呢幾日訓訓下都會無啦啦自己喊</blockquote><br />\n我都係 第一日喊到做緊咩都喊緊<br />\n宜家就係見到咩都諗起我地一齊做緊果樣野既回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc500b88839cdbbc48f6bd688c85ed5f411ff6ff","tid":441444,"uid":95759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T22:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學識打「玩法」就放低到</blockquote><br />\n玩法玩法玩法<br />\n係咪得架啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b5e57c52c626fb3f7da439c4cfd2901fbc6053","tid":441444,"uid":61913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T00:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>共勉之<br />\n我都係琴日分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵啲野做下比自己散心<br />\n你有冇自己嘅興趣？<br />\n可能你地一齊果陣 你有嘅興趣放低左<br />\n依家可以拎翻起啲興趣<br />\n同埋可以嘅話 同朋友傾下計 比自己放鬆下<br />\n連登都仲有好多人可以陪你傾計啊</blockquote><br />\n最緊要真係唔好將啲負面情緒收收埋埋<br />\n搵朋友傾又好<br />\n飲下酒又好<br />\n一定要講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喊到雙眼皮都冇埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喊夠啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱分手,唔需要迫自己將情緒收埋,反而應該由得佢表露出嚟<br />\n<br />\n揾朋友傾偈,講曬出嚟會舒服d<br />\n<br />\n到有一日你會發現,你點頹點傷心都好,佢嘅世界依然會繼續轉<br />\n<br />\n你好好咁享受返單身嘅日子<br />\n<br />\n有咩之前想做但因為拍拖做唔到嘅嘢,一次過做曬佢,為自己而活<br />\n<br />\n當初有咩做得唔好,改善好自己,要喺呢一次分手取得進步"},{"pid":"4e48a155ad1a5144c17debf673ef2a0593bc7b33","tid":441444,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T01:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學識打「玩法」就放低到</blockquote><br />\n玩法玩法玩法<br />\n係咪得架啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得時間幫到妳"},{"pid":"1b39e90b43b2cddcc646051d12fd89555a58a4c9","tid":441444,"uid":95759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>共勉之<br />\n我都係琴日分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵啲野做下比自己散心<br />\n你有冇自己嘅興趣？<br />\n可能你地一齊果陣 你有嘅興趣放低左<br />\n依家可以拎翻起啲興趣<br />\n同埋可以嘅話 同朋友傾下計 比自己放鬆下<br />\n連登都仲有好多人可以陪你傾計啊</blockquote><br />\n最緊要真係唔好將啲負面情緒收收埋埋<br />\n搵朋友傾又好<br />\n飲下酒又好<br />\n一定要講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喊到雙眼皮都冇埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喊夠啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱分手,唔需要迫自己將情緒收埋,反而應該由得佢表露出嚟<br />\n<br />\n揾朋友傾偈,講曬出嚟會舒服d<br />\n<br />\n到有一日你會發現,你點頹點傷心都好,佢嘅世界依然會繼續轉<br />\n<br />\n你好好咁享受返單身嘅日子<br />\n<br />\n有咩之前想做但因為拍拖做唔到嘅嘢,一次過做曬佢,為自己而活<br />\n<br />\n當初有咩做得唔好,改善好自己,要喺呢一次分手取得進步</blockquot