r />\n<br />\n你好好咁享受返單身嘅日子<br />\n<br />\n有咩之前想做但因為拍拖做唔到嘅嘢,一次過做曬佢,為自己而活<br />\n<br />\n當初有咩做得唔好,改善好自己,要喺呢一次分手取得進步</blockquote><br />\n今日見到佢好似頹都唔頹下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪得我一個咁on9自己喺度亂諗<br />\n點解咁唔公平</blockquote><br />\n頹個面唔比人睇姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最得意係佢朝早好頹 明顯到比曬全世界睇<br />\n轉個頭就好似乜事都冇有講有笑<br />\n仲繼續喺我面前同其他囡開開心心咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪我太多餘</blockquote><br />\n可能同女女傾計係佢麻醉自己既方法姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然，都有可能係佢頹比人睇係想引女女關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d4687fd27c2e9c48cd6375b48aebf2bad8f5f6","tid":441444,"uid":95759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n最緊要真係唔好將啲負面情緒收收埋埋<br />\n搵朋友傾又好<br />\n飲下酒又好<br />\n一定要講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喊到雙眼皮都冇埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喊夠啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱分手,唔需要迫自己將情緒收埋,反而應該由得佢表露出嚟<br />\n<br />\n揾朋友傾偈,講曬出嚟會舒服d<br />\n<br />\n到有一日你會發現,你點頹點傷心都好,佢嘅世界依然會繼續轉<br />\n<br />\n你好好咁享受返單身嘅日子<br />\n<br />\n有咩之前想做但因為拍拖做唔到嘅嘢,一次過做曬佢,為自己而活<br />\n<br />\n當初有咩做得唔好,改善好自己,要喺呢一次分手取得進步</blockquote><br />\n今日見到佢好似頹都唔頹下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪得我一個咁on9自己喺度亂諗<br />\n點解咁唔公平</blockquote><br />\n頹個面唔比人睇姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最得意係佢朝早好頹 明顯到比曬全世界睇<br />\n轉個頭就好似乜事都冇有講有笑<br />\n仲繼續喺我面前同其他囡開開心心咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪我太多餘</blockquote><br />\n可能同女女傾計係佢麻醉自己既方法姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然，都有可能係佢頹比人睇係想引女女關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢本身都同啲女玩得好埋<br />\n係我一直縱容佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日都仲對住<br />\n點先可以過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ae68d13da5d98d89a3cde19f9a8377c125e7a8","tid":441444,"uid":18144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩今日星期五聽日就放假了<br />\n分手後仲要返工原來真係會笑唔出<br />\n平時同無拍拖都無分別 覺得生活如常<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但要係咁提自己已經無男朋友要過番單身生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df589b7e12ed85166695493117d606826d411d0","tid":441444,"uid":95759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩今日星期五聽日就放假了<br />\n分手後仲要返工原來真係會笑唔出<br />\n平時同無拍拖都無分別 覺得生活如常<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但要係咁提自己已經無男朋友要過番單身生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好唔好彩地係同佢同班<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n日日見住"},{"pid":"ae859575be10fa70f6064950673aeac0392c7e21","tid":441444,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩今日星期五聽日就放假了<br />\n分手後仲要返工原來真係會笑唔出<br />\n平時同無拍拖都無分別 覺得生活如常<img src=\"/asset