 />\n因為佢好似冇事仲好開心咁<br />\n所以我叫自己千祈唔好喺佢面前比佢見到我頹既一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能大家鬥扮無嘢呢！</blockquote><br />\n我都寧願係咁<br />\n但係佢既頹只不過係因為冇左個人錫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而唔係因爲我"},{"pid":"746ac6cf95017f2054e35b2783e47bacd412ad6e","tid":441444,"uid":95759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T14:09:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊的吾去，新的不來</blockquote><br />\n冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  愛情呢家野真係可能唔岩我玩<br />\n或者係我根本唔會遇到好男人"},{"pid":"6730f7ff57ae305a1fc4b848eacb466981a3c553","tid":441444,"uid":95759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T14:10:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩今日星期五聽日就放假了<br />\n分手後仲要返工原來真係會笑唔出<br />\n平時同無拍拖都無分別 覺得生活如常<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但要係咁提自己已經無男朋友要過番單身生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好唔好彩地係同佢同班<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n日日見住</blockquote><br />\n眼鳩冤</blockquote><br />\n因為佢好似冇事仲好開心咁<br />\n所以我叫自己千祈唔好喺佢面前比佢見到我頹既一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前試過<br />\n學都唔敢番<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分手之後第一日冇返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係知道遲早都要面對"},{"pid":"46bb6e85c64d11efd74f75ad4cdfd9f0e682ed0a","tid":441444,"uid":12783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T14:28:18.000Z","msg":"我都散左，自己唔識拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 逼得太緊。到知自己問題已經太遲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又或者我可能比人帽左都未頂。<br />\n<br />\n分手理由係：拍拖太攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n佢啲野我唔會dum 唔會del 始終都係一份回憶 <br />\n佢改變左我既性格同價值觀 令我變得愈來愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遺憾同你續唔到前緣"},{"pid":"3d8b26fcbaca38a1dadf0e1fdd77c86b251a3cb9","tid":441444,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"做運動啦<br />\n可以療傷同嗰人開心好多"}]}